              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="2ecd-b4ff-9e78-a8e2">A model with the Hellfly Host Strain replaces their Movement Characteristic with 6”/Flying and gains the FLYING Keyword. In addition, a model with the Hellfly Host Strain loses the Undead Fortitude ability.</characteristic>
